        lat: 47.10, lng: -122.63, overseas: false,
        president: "William Al Jackson",
        description: "Formed to bring together people assigned to or living near Joint Base Lewis-McChord, Washington. Membership is open to retirees and active duty personnel of all services, current or former government civilians, and anyone associated with the US Army Chemical Corps.",
